	<p><blockquote><span class="smallfont">Quote:</span><hr size="1" /><i>Originally posted by Latitare </i><br />
<b>I'm interested to hear what you would do Lurikeen.<br />
<br />
<br />
What is your cure for the US economy ??<br />
<br />
Would you have pressured the Fed to drop rates ??<br />
<br />
Would you have pressured Congress to lower taxes ??<br />
<br />
Let's hear the grand Lurikeen plan to fix everything.<br />
<br />
Someone very wise once told me that you should never complain about any situation unless you are able to offer a realistic solution to that situation. </b><hr size="1" /></blockquote><br />
You should listen to wise people more often. Then you wouldn't look like a complete and utter gimp.<br />
<br />
I would pull our troops out of Europe and out of the Middle East as quickly as I could and reallocate those resources to defending our borders with a true homeland security. In fact, I would pull our troops out of every theatre and leave countries alone! If they need our help, then let them come to us and ask. <br />
<br />
I would cut government spending and increase taxes to pay off the deficit. I would continue to support the Fed in their managment of rates. I would axe the Office of Homeland Security. That is the most bloated beauracracy we have at the moment. Next would be a large downsizing of the IRS (involving the abolition of tax audits on those making under 100K per year).<br />
<br />
Pulling back our troops around the world, downsizing government, cutting spending, and increasing taxes would quickly eliminate the deficit and bring up the economy.<br />
<br />
But, I am not in power and can't do such nifty things now can I.</p>
	
	
	
